snippet.title: Best VGM 1204 - Kirby's Epic Yarn - Grass Land
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 786 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qs3lqJnkMX8
Best VGM 1010 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BMpvrfwD7Hg

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Nintendo Wii
Kirby's Epic Yarn (2010)
Grass Land
Jun Ishikawa, Hirokazu Ando, Shogo Sakai & Tadashi Ikegami
